## 📱 Support Responsive

### Breakpoints Tailwind
```
Mobile:  xs (< 640px)    → 1 colonne
Tablet:  md (768px)      → 2 colonnes
Desktop: lg (1024px)     → 3-4 colonnes
Large:   xl (1280px+)    → 4 colonnes
```

### Adaptation
- Stats Cards: 1 → 2 → 4 colonnes
- Content: 1 colonne → 2/3 + 1/3
- Sidebar: Dropdown → Visible
- Navigation: N/A

